{"tid":1365543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益  召集30萬市民罷工罷市","createTime":"2019-07-25T16:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T01:23:27.000Z","uid":92875,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4b62cd0b94f586608774bbe3279b476815f903c6","tid":1365543,"uid":92875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:16:43.000Z","msg":"自6月9日反送中運動開始，已經好多人話罷工罷市，最成功一次係6月12日，因為呢日係最關𨫡一日，隨時就係呢日通過咗送中條例，但之後都無一日係成功罷工，現在係討論如何成功說服廣大市民一齊罷工。<br />\n<br />\n首先要講吓點解無人響應罷工，可以用博弈論嘅囚徒困境去解釋。用其實市民唔係唔想罷工，而係好多人都諗網上係好多人支持，但如果當日公司得自己一個罷工，咁我咪好on99，又做唔到個效果，而自己又浪費一日annual或sick leave。所以我就諗咗一個方法去說服市民罷工。<br />\n<br />\n第一步定咗邊一日同最少幾多人要罷工，暫定8月5日先及30萬人（現在勞動人口有360萬人，30萬佔不足10%，但呢個係相對有效果而容易達到即目標）。然後搵一個平台（例如Google Form）去叫人去登記支持罷工，只需要留email就可以。最重要係<span style=\"color: red;\">支持人數係30萬以下不發動罷工，30萬以上先罷工，即是30萬人一係一齊罷，一係唔罷</span>（有少少費話feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n跟住就要宣傳出去，首要目標唔係你親朋戚友，而係你同事。假如10個人唔返工，10分佈唔同公司同10個都係同一公司嘅效果分別就好大。所以首先同事，再到朋友，家人。<br />\n<br />\n你哋覺得有無得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：80後廢中cdrom"},{"pid":"546bc16b022cb063d133527b1cdfa4d0480251a8","tid":1365543,"uid":92875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:19:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6aa3172a8ccbf93c074950fbf7c84c8f705c86f0","tid":1365543,"uid":73826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:20:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sv8PDPb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsv8PDPb.jpg&h=c4f75dab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc4a6c22ba4a89299775399ac0ea1e6c67925da1","tid":1365543,"uid":92875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:23:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4412611934ed7c95258e95be1066e69308a40241","tid":1365543,"uid":271407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:52:01.000Z","msg":"要一齊罷工啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ba359b90956740e455eba9dbd95366b393b178","tid":1365543,"uid":72597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:59:04.000Z","msg":"高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推爆佢"},{"pid":"4d2ca9252f7490dc174b294b0def4e4e716a5a5d","tid":1365543,"uid":72597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:04:10.000Z","msg":"最好係分有寫明咩機構，然後只留名（optionally外加一句個間公司啲人先知/明的說話，等大家辨識到堅係自己人），啲人會需要匿名地有共識知道自己公司大約幾多人一齊罷<br />\n跟住email係hidden and only for verification <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1757295b02049529e36552cdc5a830812780cb","tid":1365543,"uid":92875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T22:35:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1b0655170a948bf52fad63e7a3a178b9710f94e1","tid":1365543,"uid":92875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T22:38:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c5c8d8c6378b905b11455070a41dec09253bbc8","tid":1365543,"uid":92875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T22:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5598df20a53f61080cfd91315d22956fe9b9a5d","tid":1365543,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T22:43:13.000Z","msg":"得罪講句,3萬人都唔知有無"},{"pid":"c20a037178be0fccf59f9c1e3fc7fa59c9e349dd","tid":1365543,"uid":92875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5598df20a53f61080cfd91315d22956fe9b9a5d","tid":1365543,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T22:43:13.000Z","msg":"得罪講句,3萬人都唔知有無"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime